videos.description: Damarea Crockett's number gets called on 2nd-and-goal, as he pounds in a 2-yard Missouri touchdown.
videos.headline: Missouri motors in 2-yard TD

videos.description: Missouri RB Larry Rountree III cuts back, fights through tacklers and breaks the plane for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Missouri RB plunges in goal-line TD

videos.description: Missouri's defense gets a huge 4th-and-1 stop in its own territory, as Kentucky RB Asim Rose is stopped in his tracks.
videos.headline: Missouri stuffs Kentucky on huge goal-line stop

videos.description: Corey Fatony shags the sky-high punt, weaves through traffic, and zooms into the end zone for a 57-yard punt return, narrowing Missouri's lead to 14-9.
videos.headline: Wildcats get back in game with 57-yard punt return

videos.description: With less than 3 minutes to play and trailing 14-9, Terry Wilson returns from his benching and is picked off on an overthrow by DeMarkus Acy.
videos.headline: Kentucky QB airmails interception

videos.description: Kentucky QB Terry Wilson flings a 2-yard touchdown dart to C.J. Conrad on the last play of the game to come back and defeat Missouri 15-14.
videos.headline: Kentucky downs Missouri on walk-off TD pass

videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops loves the way his team fought back to defeat Missouri on the last play of regulation.
videos.headline: Stoops says he's proud of Wilson, team's resiliency

videos.description: C.J. Conrad says he told QB Terry Wilson to "put it on me" before his game-winning 2-yard touchdown to defeat Missouri on the last play of regulation.
videos.headline: Conrad on TD grab: 'I'm gonna win this game'

videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops celebrated his win over Missouri by crowd surfing his players.
